Invocation Name: number lookup
des:
Use Number Lookup to discover who is behind that phone call. Each lookup will fetch the caller's name, caller id, carrier, timezone, location, robo-call risk ranking and more. Not all numbers will have all the details.

To use Number Lookup you'll have to purchase a Number Lookup Subscription. Your subscription provides unlimited lookups. Pruchasing is simple with voice driven In-Skill Pruchasing. Prime Members save on thier first purchase.

Number Lookup uses paid public services to find the detials about US and Canadian phone numbers. All the details Number Lookup exposes can be discovered by anyone with a credit card.

Enable the HP Alexa Skill if you would like to print the Number Lookup report. Attempting to print without the HP Alexa Skill enabled will appear to begin working, but will ultimately fail.

If you have an questions or suggestions, please contact us at admin@voicefocused.com
